# Agent Prompts — Hero Build

One prompt per agent. Each prompt is copy-paste ready. Run Cards 1–9 in parallel, then Card 10 last.

**Plan file path (referenced in every prompt):**
`./HERO_BUILD_PLAN.md`

**Output convention:**
- Cards 1–9 write a fragment to `./parts/card_N.html` containing `<style>` + HTML markup.
- Card 10 reads all fragments and produces `./hero.html`.

**Rules every agent follows:**
1. Read CARD 0 in the plan file before doing anything else.
2. Read only your assigned card.
3. Use the CSS variables from CARD 0 — do not hardcode hex codes outside the `:root` block.
4. Inline all SVGs. No external icon libraries.
5. No JS unless the card explicitly requires it.
6. After writing the fragment, re-read it once and verify every acceptance criterion in your card.

